data.description: HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! Priced below appraisal! Assumable loan with 4.75% interest rate may be possible... Move in ready, just in time for Christmas!! Within walking distance of the schools. This house has been completely remodeled down to the foundation! Yep, even a new foundation! Freshly landscaped with auto sprinklers for your ease. **If you're looking for a short term rental, this is available. Renters will have first option to buy, will need first and last months rent ($1800) and $1000 deposit. Will need to provide credit report and rental history. Deposit will be returned upon move out as long as home is clean and well maintained.
